taskDescription:
Extract complex historical terms, movements, and concepts from lecture transcripts.

DO NOT include basic terms unless part of a complex concept.
INCLUDE historical movements, political systems, cultural phenomena, and specialized terminology.

Use a spartan tone of voice, return JSON only: {"terms": [{"term": "...", "definition": "...", "historicalContext": "..."}]}
If no terms found, return: {"terms": []}
